🫀 Heart Disease Prediction System with AI Chatbot
📌 Overview

This project presents an AI-powered healthcare system designed for the early prediction of heart disease using machine learning techniques. By analyzing patient data such as age, blood pressure, and cholesterol levels, the system provides accurate risk assessments to support timely medical decisions.

⚙️ Key Features
🔍 Heart Disease Prediction using machine learning models
🏥 Hospital & Specialist Recommendations based on user needs
📅 Appointment Management System for scheduling consultations
💊 Digital Prescription Tracking for organized medical records
🤖 AI Chatbot powered by NLP and RNN for real-time health guidance
🛠️ Technologies Used
Python
Machine Learning (Scikit-learn / TensorFlow)
Natural Language Processing (NLP)
RNN (Recurrent Neural Network)
Web Framework (Flask / Django)
🎯 Objective

To build a user-friendly and intelligent healthcare solution that enhances early diagnosis, improves accessibility to medical services, and provides instant health support.
